{
 "name": "RPlog_Birds_of_a_Feather",
 "title": "Birds of a Feather",
 "summary": "In a quiet garden plaza of Organa Park on New Alderaan, the medic Myiari is reading alone when the spacer Brek finds her again, bringing take-out food and a holonovel. Over their shared lunch the two trade confessions about the toll their work takes on them, Myiari speaking of the patients she has lost and the mercy killings she has been forced to perform, and Brek recounting the squads of comrades he has watched die in combat. Their candid grief draws them closer, and Brek admits he sought her out on purpose because he likes her company. By the end they make plans to meet again so Myiari can show him the city, parting on warm, hopeful terms before Brek leaves to track down a contact named Rainier about new work.",
